<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Personalized Job Matches!</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #333; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            background-color: white; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981, #059669); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 30px 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; 
        }
        .header h1 { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 24px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
        }
        .content { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            padding: 30px 20px; 
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .job-card { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            padding: 20px; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .job-card:hover {
            border-color: #10B981;
        }
        .job-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .job-title {
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .match-badge {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            color: #059669;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .company-name {
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .job-meta {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .meta-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .job-description {
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .apply-button { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: #10B981;
            color: white; 
            padding: 10px 20px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .view-all-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #f9fafb;
            color: #111827;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        }
        .footer { 
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 30px; 
            color: #6b7280; 
            font-size: 12px; 
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #10B981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🚀 Your Personalized Job Matches!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
                <p>We found <strong>{{jobCount}}</strong> new opportunities that match your profile perfectly. Check them out below!</p>
            </div>
            
            {{#each jobs}}
            <div class="job-card">
                <div class="job-header">
                    <h3 class="job-title">{{title}}</h3>
                    <span class="match-badge">{{matchPercentage}}% Match</span>
                </div>
                <div class="company-name">🏢 {{company}}</div>
                
                <div class="job-meta">
                    <div class="meta-item">📍 {{location}}</div>
                    <div class="meta-item">💼 {{type}}</div>
                    {{#if salary}}
                    <div class="meta-item">💰 {{salary}}</div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="job-description">
                    {{description}}
                </div>
                
                <a href="{{applicationLink}}" class="apply-button">View & Apply Now</a>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #4b5563;">Don't miss out on these opportunities!</p>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="view-all-button">View All Matches in Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 40px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong style="color: #10B981;">The XCareer Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 XCareer. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You received this email based on your profile preferences and qualifications.</p>
            <p><a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#">Update Preferences</a> | <a href="#">Dashboard</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
